    "fig, (ax1,ax2) = plt.subplots(1,2, figsize=(20,10)) # set size and arange subplots\n",
    "\n",
    "sns.lineplot(x,chi2.pdf(x, 1),label='k=1', ax=ax1) # plot PDF for chi-squared distribution on the left subplot (ax1)\n",
